values: Hey LJ this weekend has been kind of cool I've chillied out with my brother Darrian and my friend mike and my gf Tiffany I met her two weeks ago and we are cool as hell she has a good personallity and we like some of the same things for instance I really didn't law and order svu unless my mom and brother were watching but I watched and actually paid attention to it and it is pretty good it was about this Nazi wanttobe's who adopted a black baby and had him killed for 70,000 dollars thats pretty messed up but I actually got into it. lol tonight New Year's Resolution comes on this is my first wwe ppv in a few months I hope its good unlike the last wwe ppv I saw o yea I decided to see if japan wrestling was any good and they are pyschotic I saw this ppv they had some many good matches I believe if they had a u.s. show wwe would be no more I mean they had these matches called death matches now one match would have been good but every match was a death match except for two they were great they were doing shit I have never ever seen in wrestling I hope they have another ppv soon please believe I will be ordering it. Me and my mom have had an ok weekend she's stays away from me and I do the same I guess u can say thats are way of getting along.I really am happy though because I found out that there is this school called fullsail that I like that I can start going to for college I did have my heart set on going to Ohio state or a scool in cali but I really do like fullsai because its strictly for music and I actually can get a degree for music production and the best part is its in Orlando and all I need is a ged so since my school stuff is all fucked up my friend told me I could go to Job corp and get my ged in a matter of 6 months I feel like thats what I might do hey who knows on monday I will give them a call and if everthing is straight than I will go from there. My goal is to be the first producer to not just do one type of music but different types of music together like trance and country something like that I really do like trance and hip hop but I also like many other types of music which will make me an even better producer and not just a one dimension producer.I want to be like rick rubin he does all kinds of music. Well my words are getting short so for now goodbye.

Whatz good lj I'm back once again here is a little insight into my head. Well things have been the same Mom still doing the same shit still not back in school lol most kids love not bein in school but it gets boring after your out for awile and its bad enough that I already failed a grade now I'm bout to fail agian I hate this shit my mom got to go to school she told me she was really good in school damn I wish I had the chancce to actually go to school in one place for most of my life I've had to pack up and move I hate living out of a fuckin suit case this shit just sucks. My mom nows I am so close to talkin to those boiz in blu but I really don't want to then I just think about what will happen to my brother I know he will hate me if I do that thats one of the reasons I just shut up and continue to let her ruin my life my this is gonna have to change sooner or later or I don't know what to do this bitch had the nerve to ask me if I  wanted to start selling crack I jus looked at her like she was stupid its bad enough she uses now she wants me to start selling it she said I wouldn't be mad if you started sellin and the she said if you get caught I pretend like I didn't know and I will get you out and everything and I know you won't believe this but she told me she wouldn't mind if I broke into houses I was pissed I just left the house because that just pissed me the fuck off I just couldn't believe she had said that but hey I guess since she does it that she figures that I will be like her but in no way or shape of form will I fuck my life up like she fucked hers up sometimes she has me feeling like fuck dis bitch she can go to hell but the sometimes she is actually caring so its kind of a crazy reletationship I don't know what to do at times my godbrotha J told me jus come up to Jersey and everything will b straight I believe him but I can't find the heart to snitch on her she not even fuckin payin the bills the fuckin phone got cut off damn! that was the only connection I had with the world besides the librarys computers and they are not open 24 hours so what the fuck thank god for comcast and Smackdown vs. Raw 06 without them I would be so fucking bored I would fuckin snap but damn I jus fuckin am about to give up I don't  know if I can handle this shit anymore especially when she keeps saying we r goin leave georgia but she continues to smoke up the moving money FUCK!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Hey folks its me again Da 1 An Only PlayBoi b.k.a (better known as) Deaven Stacy

But ne wayz that waz all good but once again when I think my parents have changed what do they do they go and fuck up and use drugs again I guess since they got my game last week they felt like they could go and get high this weekend they are really makin me think of telling my grandparents because they were gone the whole night and didn't come baq till the next day and their excuse was that my dad took this ladies car Lady(Was A friend Of theirs) took her car cause she let them hold it and my dad just snapped and went to the crack house my mom said she passed out at the house and when she came to she kept tellin my dad to leave and go home b4 it was to late but he kept gettin high he agreed or whatever that the whole thing was his fault but my point is y didn't my mom just take the car and drive off and the most fucked up thing about it was my mom said she gave him an altimatetim choose your family or drugs he chose  drugs so my mom said it was ever when they came home and He asked me should my mom leave him and I told him yes because he should'nt of chose drugs over your family I feel thats really fucked up so my mom was really pissed at him cussin him out all night then Sunday we go to church and me and my brother Darrian r sittin in  seat with our mom while my dad is up front and me and thinkin haha u have sit by your lonesome mutha fucka thats what you get then the preacher does the alter call where people go up to be prayed for so my mom goes up and me  and Darrian start talkin about his game he's gettin for his birthday which is on the 23 tuesday and then this guy I think he was a deacon comes to us and tells us we should go up with my mom for some reason and my (X)dad is layin down and my mom is kneeling beside him getting prayed for then the preacher stops prayin so me and Darrian get up going back towards our seat but my (X)dad is still prayin so my moms says wait we are are going back to our seats as A family I swear to you I was tha maddest person in that church and my mom knew that she kept say ing deaven wats wrong wats wrong knowin wats wrong me im sayin if some one keeps treatin you  shit y the hell are you going to go back with that same person the way I feel right now is if he hurts her again thats on her because I told her he keeps doing shit to u not caring I mean if he cared would he have chosen drugs over us so they are all lovey dubby and shit I haven said as much as a sentence to him and don't plan to how the fucj can you choose a mutha fuckin drug over your damn family? O yea then if this shit isn't enough this girl that I really really like started fuckin makin up bull shit lies about me tryin to go with her friend  when she knows I don't like  any of her friends first she tells me she didn't remeber askin her out and her saying yes so when she was telling me these bull shit lies I jus hung up on her and don't even plan to call her baq I feel like fuck her if your gonna do me dirty like that I shouldn't b talkin to u besides at my new school I met this really cool girl shes really nice we are friends and we get along real good I helped her when her boyfriend was treatin her like shit I always right her notes in class if I don't she won't talk to me for the rest of the day I really want to go with her but she feels like she might get hurt again and so do I its like we were both going through the same shit at the same time her man was trippin and Bridget was trippin wit me besides long distance relationships neva work out. Like right now I jus want a girl who understands some of the shit I deal wit how I move around a lot how my parents are like a girl James because he understands all the shit I go through we been cool since 6th he's the only friend that I've talk to everytime I move and he kmoes all my girlfriends he gots my baq and he sure as hell knows  I got his and I can alwayz talk to him about shit  u really can't tell people  if I met a girl like that I promis to myh self I would neva let her go hey maybe Cassandra's tha 1 but you neva kno. Well folks until next time. Its tha boy Deaven Stacy b.k.a Da 1 An Only PlayBoi
